column16: Jason Kubel singles on a fly ball to right fielder Milton Bradley.    Justin Morneau to 2nd.
Justin Morneau singles on a soft line drive to right fielder Milton Bradley.
Joe Mauer flies out to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.
Chris Dickerson grounds out softly, pitcher Jason Waddell to first baseman Derrek Lee.
Orlando Hudson grounds into a force out, shortstop Ryan Theriot to second baseman Mike Fontenot.    Rafael Furcal out at 2nd.
Rafael Furcal singles on a ground ball to right fielder Milton Bradley.
Juan Pierre called out on strikes.
Eric Milton called out on strikes.
